(18, '阳台自动浇水种菜盘', 7, 2, 3, 3000, '<p class="task-extend-item task-extend-kuo" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold;">种类</span>：<br/>家居产品、 其它</p><h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px;">具体要求：</h3><p>名称：自动浇水阳台种菜盘<br/>1，分为可以组合的两层：<br/>1）储水盘和种植盘。储水盘在运输过程中有可以作为盖子保护植株在物流过程中安全；<br/>2）上下两层可以紧密咬合组合起来；<br/>2，储水盘有自动集水的功能，以期实现整个装置自动灌溉（有设计参考）；<br/>3，种植盘和储水盘都平均分为6格；<br/>4，尺寸<br/>1）储水盘（盖子）－60*40*25<br/>2）种植盘－60*40*15<br/>5，成本限制：<br/>储水盘＋种植盘加在一起生产成本不能超过10元。所以建议种植盘考虑泡沫板，储水盘考虑塑料材质；<br/>6，造型要求：简介大方，有观赏性，有工业感。<br/>7，各个种菜盘之间有“链接锁扣”可以相连。<br/>备注：用途是阳台种菜一次性耗材，定期更新。</p><p class="mt10" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a target="_blank" href="http://rms.zhubajie.com/resource/redirect?key=homesite%2Ftask%2F1.jpg%2Forigine%2F1fcd57aa-e979-4107-a96c-f0d23e56abaa" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 115, 187); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;"><img src="http://rms.zhubajie.com/resource/redirect?key=homesite%2Ftask%2F1.jpg%2Forigine%2F1fcd57aa-e979-4107-a96c-f0d23e56abaa&s.w=500&s.h=370" alt="阳台自动浇水种菜盘" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle;"/></a></p><p class="mt10" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; backgroun